overview.en: The freemen's union was to create a new world in which all men had property and all freemen united. Based on the block chain technology, we record the property rights of free association -- ZYC, and distribute the property rights according to the value of contribution, so that the property rights of free association belong to every ordinary person participating in the contribution.
overview.zh: 自由人联合要创建一个人人有产、自由人联合的新世界。我们基于区块链技术记录自由人联合的产权——ZYC，并按贡献值进行产权分配，让自由人联合的产权属于参与贡献的每个普通人。
